        "timestamp": "2018-07-06 13:12:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> > Should these changes also be reflected in the beijing template?\n > \n > Do these changes look good?  If so, I can update the Beijing\n > template, too.  I should note, though, that the last time I looked\n > at the Beijing template, it had a number of shortcomings (can't\n > remember if it was outright bugs, or just missing functionality).\n\nYes, these changes look great! I would agree about the Beijing template, I think there have been a few updates to the Amsterdam template that were not reflected in the Beijing template prior to this. Perhaps cleaning up the Beijing template should be a separate JIRA task?",
